### LabVerse Android App - Tag API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://10.0.2.2:8080/v1/api/tags/
### Note: 10.0.2.2 is the Android emulator's alias for localhost

@baseUrl = http://10.0.2.2:8080/v1/api/tags
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@paperId = YOUR_PAPER_ID_HERE
@tagId = YOUR_TAG_ID_HERE

### 1. Get Tags by Paper ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/paper/{{paperId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get Tag by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{tagId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get All Tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/all
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

